# Volpi: Capitani - Vert Capital

# First install

- You can install it using: `poetry install` - (Para instalar as dependências do projeto)
- Run `poetry run python manage.py migrate` to create the database - (Para criar o BD)
- Rum project with `poetry run python manage.py runserver`

# Iniciar Zookeeper

- Run with `bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties`

# Iniciar Kafka

- Run with `bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties`

# Admin interface

- Browse to `http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/` to view the admin interface - (Para a Interface de utilização do admin)
